net.tridentsdk.api.perf

Class DelegatedAddTakeQueue<E>

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.tridentsdk.api.perf.DelegatedAddTakeQueue<E>
  • Type Parameters:
    E - the element type in the queue
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    AddTakeQueue<E>

    public abstract class DelegatedAddTakeQueue<E>
extends java.lang.Object
implements AddTakeQueue<E>
    Delegates insertions and takes from an AddTakeQueue to a given BlockingQueue

    Adds are handled with BlockingQueue.offer(Object), and takes are handled with the take method.

    Depending on the implementation (which may vary), the take method may or may not block or return a non-null value.

    See Also:
    AddTakeQueue, BlockingQueue
